    "date": "7-12-2020",
    "content": "<div class=\"kvgmc6g5 cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-49256 aligncenter\" src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Artboard-7-copy-2-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1161\" height=\"800\" /></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t23/2/16/1f381.png\" alt=\"🎁\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span><span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/ta4/2/16/1f382.png\" alt=\"🎂\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span>Sinh nhật là phải có quà <span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/ta4/2/16/1f382.png\" alt=\"🎂\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span><span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t23/2/16/1f381.png\" alt=\"🎁\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span></div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><strong>Pizza Express</strong> khuyến mãi tưng bừng – Mừng sinh nhật bạn</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tdd/2/16/1f50a.png\" alt=\"🔊\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span> Pizza Express muốn dành tặng bạn ưu đãi SHOCK trong ngày sinh nhật của bạn &#8211; Vui bung nóc cùng Pizza Express nào ️<span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t2b/2/16/1f389.png\" alt=\"🎉️\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span><span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t53/2/16/1f38a.png\" alt=\"🎊️\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span>️<span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t2b/2/16/1f389.png\" alt=\"🎉️\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span><span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t53/2/16/1f38a.png\" alt=\"🎊\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t10/2/16/2734.png\" alt=\"✴️\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span><span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t10/2/16/2734.png\" alt=\"✴️\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span><strong>PIZZA EXPRESS TẶNG NGAY 01 BÁNH PIZZA (SIZE S) VÀ 1 COCA COLA 390ML</strong><span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t10/2/16/2734.png\" alt=\"✴️\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span><span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t10/2/16/2734.png\" alt=\"✴️\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">Chương trình áp dụng với khách hàng:</div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4b/2/16/1f4cc.png\" alt=\"📌\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span>Có sinh nhật trùng với ngày đặt bánh.</div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4b/2/16/1f4cc.png\" alt=\"📌\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span>Đơn hàng từ 399k trở lên.</div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4b/2/16/1f4cc.png\" alt=\"📌\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span><strong>Vui lòng cung cấp mã code &#8220;SN12&#8221; cho nhân viên khi đặt bánh.</strong></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">Còn chờ gì nữa, team nhà mình hãy nhanh tay nhấc điện thoại lên và gọi cho Pizza Express ngay nào !</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/te/2/16/1f6ab.png\" alt=\"🚫\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span> Lưu Ý: Không áp dụng đồng thời các chương trình khuyến mãi khác.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/tf0/2/16/1f449.png\" alt=\"👉\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /> </span>Liên hệ tổng đài tư vấn (024) 36.888.777</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"o9v6fnle cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x c1et5uql ii04i59q\">\n<div dir=\"auto\">Pizza Express Vietnam HIỆN CÓ 5 CƠ SỞ TẠI HÀ NỘI:</div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t46/2/16/1f3ea.png\" alt=\"🏪\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span>CS1: 107D3 Ngọc Khánh, Ba Đình, Hà Nội</div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t46/2/16/1f3ea.png\" alt=\"🏪\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span>CS2: 14 Ngõ 497 Nguyễn Trãi, Thanh Xuân, Hà Nội</div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t46/2/16/1f3ea.png\" alt=\"🏪\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span>CS3: Số 6 Đồng Bát, Cầu Giấy, Hà Nội.</div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t46/2/16/1f3ea.png\" alt=\"🏪\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span>CS4: 52 Kim Đồng, Hoàng Mai, Hà Nội.</div>\n<div dir=\"auto\"><span class=\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\"><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t46/2/16/1f3ea.png\" alt=\"🏪\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></span>CS5: 69 Ngõ 2 Ngọc Thụy, Long Biên, Hà Nội.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
